                            <comment id="471726" author="stancheff" created="Wed, 17 Sep 2025 02:50:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is a test issue, do_facet mds1 &amp;lt;blah&amp;gt; is insufficient to setup job stats and collect from all targets.&lt;br/&gt;
So sometimes all the activity is on mds2 (MDT0001 and MDT0003) and since these were not setup no jobs are found.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: onyx-142vm10 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param jobid_var=procname_uid jobid_name=%e.%u
jobid_var=procname_uid
jobid_name=%e.root
CMD: onyx-142vm10 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param mdt.*.job_cleanup_interval=5
mdt.lustre-MDT0000.job_cleanup_interval=5
mdt.lustre-MDT0002.job_cleanup_interval=5
CMD: onyx-142vm10 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param mdt.*.job_stats=clear
mdt.lustre-MDT0000.job_stats=clear
mdt.lustre-MDT0002.job_stats=clear
CMD: onyx-142vm10 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param mdt.*.job_cleanup_interval=0
mdt.lustre-MDT0000.job_cleanup_interval=0
mdt.lustre-MDT0002.job_cleanup_interval=0
CMD: onyx-142vm10 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param mdt.*.job_stats | grep job_id: | cut -d. -f2
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="456643" author="adilger" created="Mon, 19 May 2025 19:38:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like test_205l added by patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/56607&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/56607&lt;/a&gt; (&quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18351&quot; title=&quot;Job stats scaling&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18351&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-18351&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; obdclass: jobstat scaling&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;) has been failing intermittently since before it landed. One failure on 2024-10-11 before it landed on 2024-12-16, and then a slow burn of failures since 2924-12-19 (a few per week).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=stancheff&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;stancheff&quot;&gt;stancheff&lt;/a&gt; could you please take a look. I don&apos;t know if this is just a test script issue, or a problem with the code itself. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
